51
00:02:33.020 --> 00:02:34.386
COUPLE OF BUCKS.

52
00:02:34.455 --> 00:02:36.388
OKAY. DIME.

53
00:02:36.457 --> 00:02:38.457
YOU GUYS SHOULD
PROBABLY KEEP TALKING.

54
00:02:38.492 --> 00:02:39.958
