DID YOU MAKE ANY NEW FRIENDS?

494
00:20:11.511 --> 00:20:14.212
YEAH. YEAH. I MET THIS WOMAN.

495
00:20:14.280 --> 00:20:15.213
OKAY. WHOA. WHOA.

496
00:20:15.281 --> 00:20:16.614
WHAT'S SHE LIKE?

497
00:20:16.683 --> 00:20:17.915
UH. WELL...

498
00:20:17.983 --> 00:20:21.252
SHE'S REALLY GOOD IN BED.

499
00:20:21.321 --> 00:20:23.621
JOEY. I THOUGHT YOU
WERE GOING TO TRY

500
00:20:23.690 --> 00:20:25.022
TO BE FRIENDS FIRST.

501
00:20:25.091 --> 00:20:27.391
WELL. HEY. IT'S ALL YOUR FAULT.

502
00:20:27.460 --> 00:20:28.604
WHAT? WHY?

503
00:20:28.628 --> 00:20:30.138
BECAUSE YOU DIDN'T
GIVE ME ADVICE.

504
00:20:30.162 --> 00:20:31.707
NO. YOU GAVE ME A PICKUP LINE.

505
00:20:31.731 --> 00:20:33.097
AS SOON AS I TOLD HER

506
00:20:33.165 --> 00:20:36.367
I WANTED TO BUILD A
FOUNDATION AND BE FRIENDS FIRST

507
00:20:36.436 --> 00:20:38.769
I SUDDENLY... THROUGH
NO FAULT OF MY OWN...

508
00:20:38.838 --> 00:20:40.504
BECAME IRRESISTIBLE TO HER.

509
00:20:40.573 --> 00:20:43.040
AND HER ROOMMATE.

510
00:20:44.377 --> 00:20:46.977
WHAT ABOUT THE CLOSENESS?

511
00:20:47.046 --> 00:20:48.279
CLOSENESS. SCHMOSENESS.

512
00:20:48.348 --> 00:20:50.481
THERE WAS THREE OF
US. FOR CRYING OUT LOUD.

513
00:20:55.921 --> 00:20:57.988
ALL RIGHT. HEY. WHO WANTS PIZZA?

514
00:20:58.057 --> 00:20:58.789
I DO. I DO. I DO.

515
00:20:58.858 --> 00:21:00.124
OH. THIS IS GREAT.

516
00:21:00.192 --> 00:21:03.461
CAN YOU BELIEVE I FOUND
THIS ON THE SECOND FLOOR?

517
00:21:06.466 --> 00:21:07.632
WHO IS IT?

518
00:21:07.700 --> 00:21:09.166
Man: N.Y.P.D.

519
00:21:09.235 --> 00:21:10.401
OH. MY GOD.

520
00:21:10.470 --> 00:21:13.404
UH... JUST A MINUTE. OFFICER!

521
00:21:22.848 --> 00:21:25.015
I'M LOOKING FOR PHOEBE BUFFAY.

522
00:21:25.084 --> 00:21:26.450
OH. MY GOD. IT'S HIM.

523
00:21:26.519 --> 00:21:27.585
IT'S THAT COP.

524
00:21:27.654 --> 00:21:29.465
GOD. I CAN'T BELIEVE
IT. HE FOUND ME.

525
00:21:29.489 --> 00:21:30.532
MY GOD. PHOEBE.

526
00:21:30.556 --> 00:21:31.933
ARE YOU GOING TO GO TO JAIL?

527
00:21:31.957 --> 00:21:35.125
WELL. IF I'M GOING DOWN. YOU
GUYS ARE GOING DOWN WITH ME.

528
00:21:35.194 --> 00:21:36.860
WHAT?

529
00:21:36.929 --> 00:21:38.262
HARBORING A FUGITIVE?

530
00:21:38.331 --> 00:21:40.398
THAT'S ONE-TO-THREE
YEARS MINIMUM.

531
00:21:40.466 --> 00:21:42.132
GOOD LUCK. CHANDLER.

532
00:21:46.439 --> 00:21:48.651
OKAY. YOU CAN ARREST
ME. FINE. BUT YOU'LL

533
00:21:48.675 --> 00:21:50.452
NEVER MAKE IT STICK.
AND YOU KNOW IT.

534
00:21:50.476 --> 00:21:52.154
YEAH. BUT I KIND OF
DON'T HAVE A CHOICE.

535
00:21:52.178 --> 00:21:53.989
IT'S MY JOB. I MEAN.
YOU UNDERSTAND. RIGHT?

536
00:21:54.013 --> 00:21:56.980
YEAH. AS LONG AS YOU UNDERSTAND
THAT I'M GOING TO CALL MY LAWYER

537
00:21:57.049 --> 00:21:58.594
AND. ONCE HE PUTS
YOU ON THE STAND

538
00:21:58.618 --> 00:22:01.018
HE'S GOING TO MAKE YOU
LOOK LIKE A FOOL... LIKE A<i> FOOL.</i>

539
00:22:01.086 --> 00:22:04.855
MM-HMM. I DON'T
LIKE LOOKING FOOLISH.

540
00:22:04.924 --> 00:22:07.491
YOU KNOW WHAT? MAYBE.
UH. I DON'T ARREST YOU TODAY.

541
00:22:07.560 --> 00:22:09.520
MAYBE I CAME BY AND
YOU WEREN'T HERE.

542
00:22:09.562 --> 00:22:11.862
I WOULD<i> LOVE</i> IT
IF I WEREN'T HERE.

543
00:22:11.931 --> 00:22:14.598
OKAY. SINCE. UM. YOU'RE
NOT GOING TO JAIL TONIGHT

544
00:22:14.667 --> 00:22:16.667
I WAS WONDERING
IF YOU WOULD LIKE

545
00:22:16.736 --> 00:22:18.101
TO GO TO DINNER WITH ME.

546
00:22:18.170 --> 00:22:19.437
ME?

547
00:22:19.505 --> 00:22:21.038
YEAH.

548
00:22:21.106 --> 00:22:23.040
EVER SINCE YOU
FLASHED MY BADGE AT ME

549
00:22:23.108 --> 00:22:25.175
I KIND OF CAN'T STOP
THINKING ABOUT YOU.

550
00:22:25.244 --> 00:22:28.346
YOU'RE THE PRETTIEST FAKE
UNDERCOVER WHORE I'VE EVER SEEN.

551
00:22:29.949 --> 00:22:32.750
NICE. NICE.

552
00:22:34.086 --> 00:22:35.820
WOW. I DIDN'T SEE THAT COMING.

553
00:22:35.888 --> 00:22:37.120
YOU'RE ASKING ME OUT.

554
00:22:37.189 --> 00:22:38.222
YEAH. AND I COULD

555
00:22:38.290 --> 00:22:39.290
HAVE DONE IT BETTER

556
00:22:39.359 --> 00:22:40.791
BUT THESE PEOPLE
KEEP STARING AT ME.

557
00:22:40.860 --> 00:22:42.526
UM... YEAH.

558
00:22:42.595 --> 00:22:46.163
I-I'D LIKE TO GO OUT
WITH YOU. OFFICER.

559
00:22:46.232 --> 00:22:47.832
GARY.

560
00:22:47.900 --> 00:22:48.833
GARY.

561
00:22:48.901 --> 00:22:51.001
OKAY. SO IT'S A DATE?

562
00:22:51.070 --> 00:22:52.514
YEAH. OOH. I GOT TO
ASK YOU. THOUGH...

563
00:22:52.538 --> 00:22:53.915
HOW DID YOU KNOW
WHERE TO FIND ME?

564
00:22:53.939 --> 00:22:55.617
WELL. YOUR FINGERPRINTS
WERE ALL OVER MY BADGE

565
00:22:55.641 --> 00:22:57.085
SO I JUST RAN THEM
THROUGH THE COMPUTER

566
00:22:57.109 --> 00:22:58.976
AND THIS IS LISTED AS
YOUR LAST KNOWN ADDRESS

567
00:22:59.044 --> 00:22:59.977
SO I JUST CHECKED IT OUT.

568
00:23:00.045 --> 00:23:01.211
OH. IMPRESSIVE.

569
00:23:01.280 --> 00:23:02.613
NOT AS IMPRESSIVE AS YOU.

570
00:23:02.682 --> 00:23:03.792
I GOT TO TELL YOU. I
LOOKED AT YOUR RECORD

571
00:23:03.816 --> 00:23:05.816
AND YOU'VE DONE SOME
PRETTY WEIRD STUFF.

572
00:23:05.885 --> 00:23:07.685
YEAH. WE'LL TALK AT DINNER.

573
00:23:07.754 --> 00:23:10.187
OKAY. SO I'LL COME
BY IN A COUPLE HOURS

574
00:23:10.256 --> 00:23:11.288
AND PICK YOU UP?

575
00:23:11.357 --> 00:23:13.034
ALL RIGHT. I CAN'T WAIT.

576
00:23:13.058 --> 00:23:15.819
OH. AND DON'T WORRY. I'M NOT GOING
TO JUST TAKE YOU OUT FOR DOUGHNUTS.

577
00:23:18.264 --> 00:23:20.798
HE HAS A GUN.

578
00:23:26.539 --> 00:23:30.274
I'D LIKE TO RETURN THIS COUCH.

579
00:23:30.342 --> 00:23:32.309
I'M NOT SATISFIED WITH IT.

580
00:23:35.314 --> 00:23:36.814
YOU WANT TO RETURN

581
00:23:36.883 --> 00:23:38.616
THIS COUCH?

582
00:23:38.684 --> 00:23:41.819
IT'S CUT IN HALF.

583
00:23:41.888 --> 00:23:44.121
THAT'S WHAT I'M TELLING YOU.

584
00:23:44.189 --> 00:23:47.324
DID YOU CUT THIS COUCH IN HALF?

585
00:23:47.393 --> 00:23:48.859
IT'S CRAZY.

586
00:23:48.928 --> 00:23:51.395
IT<i> IS</i> CUT IN HALF.

587
00:23:51.464 --> 00:23:53.864
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

588
00:23:53.933 --> 00:23:57.100
THIS COUCH IS CUT IN HALF.

589
00:23:57.169 --> 00:24:03.240
I WOULD LIKE TO EXCHANGE IT
FOR ONE THAT IS NOT CUT IN HALF.

590
00:24:03.309 --> 00:24:07.010
WE CAN'T ACCEPT
IT IN THIS CONDITION.

591
00:24:07.079 --> 00:24:11.114
WELL.<i> I</i> CAN'T ACCEPT
IT IN THIS CONDITION.

592
00:24:11.183 --> 00:24:13.061
YOU'RE TELLING ME THIS COUCH

593
00:24:13.085 --> 00:24:15.230
WAS DELIVERED TO YOU LIKE THIS?

594
00:24:15.254 --> 00:24:18.221
LOOK. I'M A REASONABLE MAN.

595
00:24:18.290 --> 00:24:21.358
I WILL ACCEPT STORE CREDIT.

596
00:24:21.427 --> 00:24:23.572
I'LL GIVE YOU STORE CREDIT

597
00:24:23.596 --> 00:24:26.163
IN THE AMOUNT OF FOUR DOLLARS.

598
00:24:29.168 --> 00:24:30.701
I WILL TAKE IT.

599
00:24:30.770 --> 00:24:34.572
